ey)|Alex Forsyth]], American ice hockey player *1955 &ndash; [[Susan B. Horwitz]], American computer scientist and academic (d. 2014) *1955 &ndash; [[Graham Murray]], Australian rugby league player and coach (d. 2013) *[[1956]] &ndash; [[Angus Deayton]], English actor, writer, musician, comedian, and broadcaster *1956 &ndash; [[Elizabeth Strout]], American novelist and short story writer *1956 &ndash; [[Justin Welby]], English archbishop *1956 &ndash; [[Clive Woodward]], English rugby player and coach *[[1957]] &ndash; [[Michael Foale]], British-American astrophysicist and astronaut *1957 &ndash; [[Nancy Lopez]], American golfer and sportscaster *[[1958]] &ndash; [[Themos Anastasiadis]], Greek journalist and economist *1958 &ndash; [[Scott Bryce]], American actor, director, and producer *1958 &ndash; [[Margus Hanson]], Estonian lawyer and politician, 23rd [[Minister of Defence (Estonia)|Estonian Minister of Defence]] *1958 &ndash; [[Mohsen Rastani]], Iranian photographer and journalist *[[1959]] &ndash; [[Kapil Dev]], Indian Cricketer *[[1960]] &ndash; [[Paul Azinger]], American golfer and sportscaster *1960 &ndash; [[Eric Grothe, Sr.]], Australian rugby league player *1960 &ndash; [[Kari Jalonen]], Finnish ice hockey player and coach *1960 &ndash; [[Nigella Lawson]], English chef and author *1960 &ndash; [[Howie Long]], American football player and sports commentator *[[1961]] &ndash; [[Georges Jobé]], Belgian motocross racer (d. 2012) *1961 &ndash; [[Nigel Melville]], English rugby player *[[1962]] &ndash; [[Michael Houser]], American singer-songwriter and guitarist (d. 2002) *1962 &ndash; [[Kevin Rosier]], American mixed martial artist and boxer (d. 2015) *1962 &ndash; [[Vangelis Vlachos]], Greek footballer and manager *[[1963]] &ndash; [[Norm Charlton]], American baseball player and coach *1963 &ndash; [[Paul Kipkoech]], Kenyan runner (d. 1995) *1963 &ndash; [[Ian Lavery]], English miner and politician *[[1964]] &ndash; [[Charles Haley]], American football playe