'''''Land og Folk Festival''''' was an annual cultural festival in [[Denmark]] organized by ''[[Land og Folk]]'', the now-defunct daily newspaper of the [[Communist Party of Denmark]].<ref>Henrik Søndergaard and Rasmus Helles. (October 2010). [http://www.mediadem.eliamep.gr/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/Denmark.pdf Media policies and regulatory practices in a selected set of European countries], MEDIADEM. Retrieved 12 December 2014.</ref> Land og Folk Festival gathered close to 100,000 visitors annually.<ref>''[https://books.google.com/books?id=33buq89bo2QC Communisme]'', No 20-21, 1988/1989. p. 192</ref>

